000Z","msg":"秒你老母閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:51:53.000Z","msg":"我孤陋寡聞<br />\n未聽過呢隻動物"},{"pid":"2393c5028e83d1aafb8710a133500e2032c6a958","tid":1191674,"uid":34571,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"答案係!! 陳國邦 (李斯) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJebjw3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJebjw3.jpg&h=a0ee34e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2Laz5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2Laz5t.jpg&h=b15df2e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n因為馬殅丁路德於十六世紀批判當時嘅教廷同皇室, 根本無時間養動物, 而且批評教廷同皇室係silly 癡線 冇可能會發生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSilly發音就係 see Li 斯李<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我地華人社會 習慣將last name 擺前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!! 答案就係李斯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而做過李斯嘅TVB藝員就係得陳國邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!!!!!!!!答案係!!!!!!!!!陳國邦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VB5YJY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVB5YJY3.jpg&h=84f4867c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n輕鬆 謝謝大家"},{"pid":"7dc76ea56e9d5261d932a9ac87dc8bca74b2d6cb","tid":1191674,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%81%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25B8%2581%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%25BE%25B7&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW86VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=cea5445f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%81%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%B7</a><br />\n馬丁路德（Martin Luther，1483年11月10號&mdash;1546年2月18號）係一個奧古斯丁會修士、Wittenberg 大學聖經研究教授，因為佢寫嘅某啲著作立場激嬲咗教廷同皇室，尤其係幾本書好似《致德意志貴族公開書》、《教會被擄巴比倫》、《基督徒的自由》就激到教宗生虾咁跳，好多內容例如「贖罪券」、「教皇赦罪權力」重有「教會財庫」等問題都批判當時嘅教廷同皇室，最後演變成同教宗對抗，結果創立咗路德教派，即係所謂新教路德宗，係當時宗教改革浪潮入面其中一個關鍵人物。"},{"pid":"76704d9bd2d256e0893ca4741ae4ad09d3a5ca84","tid":1191674,"uid":117251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"答案係 亞視補家政"}]}